  <summary date="2019-04-09T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Freedom for Families Act

This bill modifies requirements for health savings accounts (HSAs) to (1) exclude from gross income HSA distributions paid or distributed during a period of qualified caregiving, (2) allow participation in an HSA without enrollment in a high deductible health plan, and (3) increase the contribution limit for HSAs.</summary>
